title: Washington Park Studio w/ On-Site Laundry, A/C, Elevator
posting_body: ['101 Grant Street managed by Cornerstone Apartments', 'Bedrooms:', '0', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Square Ft.:', '390', 'Price:', '$1325/mo.', 'Welcome to The Vista at Washington Park, a high rise building overlooking the beautiful neighborhood of Wash Park.', 'With a media room, fitness center, business center, and amazon lockers, this place has plenty of amenities for all of your needs!', "Located in a beautiful neighborhood of houses, you'll find dog walkers, joggers, and any assortment of active people.", 'On the weekends, take a trip to the fun Cherry Creek shopping center, a famous denver mall with a variety of stores to browse at your leisure.', 'Come visit The Vista at Washington Park today!', 'Features:', 'Storage', 'Amazon Lockers', 'Controlled Access', 'Rooftop Deck', 'Media Room', 'Coffee Machine', 'A/C Units', 'Fitness Center', 'On-Site Coinless Laundry', 'Off-Street Parking', 'Elevator', 'Communal Kitchen', 'Contact us:', 'To schedule a showing please contact our leasing team at', 'To apply NOW please visit <URL>', 'Nearby Neighborhoods:', "Baker, Five Points, LoHi, RiNo, West Wash Park, Cheesman Park, Downtown, Sloan's Lake, Congress Park, Uptown, Jefferson Park, Hale, Capitol Hill, University of Denver, Platt Park, Highlands, City Park", 'Availability and pricing are subject to change.']
